item.title: CVE-2023-47610|2024-07-22T12:20:02.536Z -- telit%20cinterion -- ehs5
item.description: A CWE-120: Buffer Copy without Checking Size of Input vulnerability exists in Telit Cinterion EHS5/6/8 that could allow a remote unauthenticated attacker to execute arbitrary code on the targeted system by sending a specially crafted SMS message.
